# Project Rules (Python RAG)

- Use lightweight Clean Architecture (domain/application/infrastructure/interfaces).
- Design for OCP: add new strategies/data sources without changing core logic.
- TDD-lite with pytest on key use cases (retriever, threshold, API contract).
- Hallucination guard: use similarity threshold and source reference;  
  when below threshold → respond with "죄송해요, 제가 가지고 있는 데이터셋에는 해당 내용이 없어요."
- FastAPI + env-driven config; suitable for free hosting (Render/Vercel).
